snippet.title: All The Boys Love Mandy Lane - Horror News - Amber Heard 2013
snippet.description:
Release Date: 9/6/13 on VOD, plus a Limited Theatrical Release in Oct.
(Film was originally completed in 2006)
Cast: Amber Heard, Anson Mount, Whitney Able, Michael Welch, Edwin Hodge, Aaron Himelstein, Luke Grimes, and Melissa Pric.

Official Synopsis: A group of high-schoolers invite Mandy Lane, a good girl who became quite hot over the summer, to a weekend party on a secluded ranch. While the festivities rage on, the number of revelers begins to drop quite mysteriously.

Commentary by JBM from VillainNews
